    "info": "The <b>Star in a Bottle<\/b> is a Lantern variant. On the <img src=\".\/data\/images\/desktop version.png\" alt=\"desktop version\" title=\"desktop version\" \/>\u00a0Desktop version, <img src=\".\/data\/images\/console version.png\" alt=\"console version\" title=\"console version\" \/>\u00a0Console version, and <img src=\".\/data\/images\/mobile version.png\" alt=\"mobile version\" title=\"mobile version\" \/>\u00a0Mobile version, it provides players in its vicinity with an increased rate of mana regeneration (about 2\/s). The buff is applied to any players standing within a rectangular area of 170\u00d7125 (<img src=\".\/data\/images\/desktop version.png\" alt=\"desktop version\" title=\"desktop version\" \/>) \/ 100\u00d784 (<span class=\"eico\"><img src=\".\/data\/images\/console version.png\" alt=\"console version\" title=\"console version\" \/>\u2009<img src=\".\/data\/images\/mobile version.png\" alt=\"mobile version\" title=\"mobile version\" \/><\/span>) tiles centered on the bottle, similar to the Campfire and Heart Lantern. Similarly to other Lanterns, the Star in a Bottle is a mechanism that can be toggled on or off if wired, though this does not affect the buff.\n",
